jadx - Dex to Java Decompiler
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Copyright 2018 skylot
Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0

RetroGrade bundles jadx (https://github.com/skylot/jadx) for DEX bytecode
decompilation. jadx is used to convert Android Dalvik bytecode back to
readable Java source code.

The full Apache 2.0 license text for jadx can be found in:
  jadx/LICENSE

Website: https://github.com/skylot/jadx

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

