Eclipse Temurin (Java Runtime)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Eclipse Temurin is the open source Java SE build based upon OpenJDK.

Licensed under the GNU General Public License, version 2, with the
Classpath Exception (GPLv2+CE).

RetroGrade bundles Eclipse Temurin JRE to provide Java runtime for
jadx decompilation without requiring users to install Java separately.

Website: https://adoptium.net/

